Package src

Class Animal

java.lang.Object
src.Animal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Animal>
public class Animal extends Object implements Comparable<Animal>
Class for animal pieces to be used in the GameBoard class. Each animal object will have their respective player faction, rank, species name, position, and state within the game, and will be stored within the Tile and Player classes.
